com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore.id.domain

Class SctId

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore.id.domain.SctId

  • public class SctId
extends Object
    Represents a SNOMED CT identifier.

    Note that properties must match the format used by SNOMED's component identifier service, as this class is also used for marshalling results via Jackson when communicating over an HTTP client.

    Since:
    4.5
